          "description": "Much respect to Trung at this CVS location! I've stopped here many times for many different things on many different occasions. Trung is an expert at not only handling many things all at once, but always maintaining a friendly and professional demeanor, no matter how crazy things get. This CVS location is very fortunate to have Trung!!!",
