        {
          "username": "Joy Han",
          "rating": 5,
          "contributor_id": "110382318076079686042",
          "user_review_count": 8,
          "user_photo_count": 3,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJwS7tutzNoBLbuCz5f8eX9DlyBtBjdn2nfXZg2l9POQJumd2o=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100",
          "description": "Paul is the nicest retail employee I\u2019ve encountered in years, and I work in retail! I know how much it can suck working late nights, especially in the city, but he was so warm and calm that I instantly felt comfortable talking to him. Not only that, he was super efficient and wasted no time helping us. The rest of the store team was nice too. I\u2019ve never written a review for a drugstore before, but Paul deserves all the recognition for great service and great work.",
